vampires vs. zombies is an independent horror film loosely based upon j. sheridan le fanu 's classic 1872 novel carmilla . unlike le fanu 's story , however , most of the action in the film takes place inside a car . the title and the cover were obviously inspired by the horror film freddy vs. jason , it 's unclear if it was intended as a mockbuster of that film or not . the movie was originally titled vampires vs. zombies , but it has since then been changed to carmilla , the lesbian vampire . vince d'amato is the director and screenwriter of this film .